OL,3,CBurglar who swam through lake and
OL,4,Cclimbed tree to evade police jailed
OL,6,FA burglar has been jailed after he
OL,7,Fattempted to evade police by swimming
OL,8,Fto an island.
OL,10,FChad Lambert, 35, of Cobourg Road,
OL,11,FBristol, was sentenced to 26 weeks in
OL,12,Fprison on Monday 21 October after he
OL,13,Fadmitted to aggravated burglary.
OL,15,FBristol Magistrates' Court heard how,
OL,16,Fon Saturday 19 October at around 1pm,
OL,17,FLambert had entered a shop on Averay
OL,18,FRoad, Bristol, and was acting
OL,19,Fsuspiciously.
