OL,4,Cclimbed tree to evade police jailed
OL,6,FWhen he was challenged by staff, he
OL,7,Fsmashed a window to get behind the
OL,8,Fcounter, picked up a bottle of wine
OL,9,Fand took the contents of the till.
OL,11,FHe ran into Eastville Park, off
OL,12,FFishponds Road, where he discarded his
OL,13,Fclothing and a bag before running into
OL,14,Fthe lake and swimming to the small
OL,15,Fisland in the middle.
OL,17,FOfficers chased after Lambert on foot
OL,18,Fand followed him to the lake.
