OL,6,FThe drone unit was deployed to assist
OL,7,Fthe officers, using the drone to
OL,8,Ffollow Lambert's movements on the
OL,9,Fisland in the foliage and directing
OL,10,Fthem to his location.
OL,12,FWith assistance from Avon Fire and
OL,13,FRescue Service, who provided a boat,
OL,14,Fthe officers were able to reach the
OL,15,Fisland and arrest Lambert.
OL,17,FHe was later charged and put before a
OL,18,Fcourt where he pleaded guilty.
OL,20,FAlong with his jail sentence, he was
OL,21,Fordered to pay #154 in compensation.
